oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Colditz General Merchandise
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph inside the dry goods department of Colditz General Merchandise. Mrs. Colditz (center) is measuring fabric on a counter. An unidentified girl and baby are seated on either side of her. Fabrics, dishes, brooms, and more can be seen on shelves in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Stores & shops; Women; Children
